content: zhourunlai: Merged 3 significant PRs this month, including adding experimental telemetry model options (#1603, +83/-99 lines), implementing the Tavily SDK (#1599, +7449/-1288 lines), and updating the Volcengine model (#1586, +7546/-1201 lines). These contributions represent substantial code additions with over 15,000 new lines across the three PRs. Activity was concentrated on a single day this month, focusing primarily on feature development work.
